# Wayfinder tracker

- Map issue labelled `wayfinder:map` is the canonical index on **`Practical-Office/bml-onboarding`**.
- Child tickets: `wayfinder:task`, `wayfinder:prototype`, `wayfinder:research`, `wayfinder:grilling`.
- Claim a ticket (assign) before work; resolve one ticket per session unless research subagents run in parallel.
- Record resolutions as issue comments; close ticket; append gist + link to map **Decisions so far**.
- Refer by **linked title**, not bare `#` numbers.
